edu.vserver.exercises.helpers
Class ExerTypeVoidImplCollection

java.lang.Object
  edu.vserver.exercises.helpers.ExerTypeVoidImplCollection

public final class ExerTypeVoidImplCollection
extends java.lang.Object

A collection of classes that can be used to give implementations that inform the user that certain aspect of the exercise-type system is not really implemented for certain exercise-type. These should of course only be used temporarily.

Author:
Riku Haavisto
